      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.YMGOKoZtKgJqIsAD]{Mechanic Trick}</p>\n<p>You are adept at making weapons look like devices of a different type. With 10 minutes of work, you can attempt an Engineering check versus a DC equal to 10 + 1-1/2 × the weapon’s level to disguise it as something mundane. If you are successful, you gain a +10 circumstance bonus to Disguise checks versus attempts to detect the true nature of the weapon.</p>"
